WEBVTT

00:01.458 --> 00:03.166
Jack:
OVER 68 MILLION AMERICANS

00:03.166 --> 00:05.208
LEAVE THE SAFETY
OF OUR BORDERS EVERY YEAR.

00:05.208 --> 00:06.875
IF DANGER STRIKES,

00:06.875 --> 00:09.166
THE FBI's
INTERNATIONAL RESPONSE TEAM

00:09.166 --> 00:11.500
IS CALLED INTO ACTION.

00:13.166 --> 00:16.500
♪♪

00:35.834 --> 00:38.000
♪♪

00:38.000 --> 00:39.667
YEAH.
THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

00:39.667 --> 00:41.834
♪♪

00:47.750 --> 00:50.750
♪♪

00:53.834 --> 00:55.834
WE HAD A VERY GOOD NIGHT,
AUNT M.

00:55.834 --> 00:57.333
HMM?

00:57.333 --> 00:58.667
I'D SAY ANY NIGHT WHERE
I DON'T HAVE TO CLEAN UP

00:58.667 --> 01:00.625
YOUR BROKEN BOTTLES IS
A GOOD NIGHT.

01:02.208 --> 01:04.375
BOYS, DANKE. YOU'VE BEEN
SUCH A GODSEND TO ME

01:04.375 --> 01:05.792
THESE PAST FEW WEEKS.

01:05.792 --> 01:07.291
NO, THANK YOU.

01:07.291 --> 01:10.166
HONESTLY, HANGING OUT HERE
HAS BEEN JUST COOL.

01:10.166 --> 01:11.792
YEAH, I MEAN, IF IT
WEREN'T FOR YOU,

01:11.792 --> 01:13.458
TIMOTHY AND I WOULD BE
STUCK SOMEWHERE

01:13.458 --> 01:15.083
IN THE MIDDLE OF GEORGIA,

01:15.083 --> 01:16.500
BULLDOZING DIRT
FOR DAD'S COMPANY.

01:16.500 --> 01:18.041
NOT EXACTLY HOW YOU'D DREAM
OF WHILING AWAY

01:18.041 --> 01:19.375
YOUR DAYS BETWEEN SEMESTERS.

01:19.375 --> 01:20.834
I'M GOING TO MISS YOU BOYS

01:20.834 --> 01:22.208
WHEN YOU HAVE TO GO BACK HOME
FOR SCHOOL.

01:22.208 --> 01:23.583
WE'LL MISS YOU, TOO.

01:23.583 --> 01:26.000
AH. GOEIE NAG, BOYS.

01:26.000 --> 01:27.667
GOOD NIGHT.
NIGHT, AUNT M.

01:27.667 --> 01:30.375
YOU KNOW, I GET WHY DAD MOVED
AWAY FROM JOHANNESBURG

01:30.375 --> 01:32.208
BACK IN THE DAY,
BUT I DON'T GET

01:32.208 --> 01:34.667
WHY HE DOESN'T LIKE
COMING BACK HERE TO VISIT.

01:34.667 --> 01:36.750
WHO KNOWS?
YOU KNOW HOW DAD IS.

01:36.750 --> 01:38.125
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

01:38.125 --> 01:39.625
I'M GONNA TAKE THE REST
OF THIS TRASH OUT.

01:39.625 --> 01:41.250
YOU NEED ME TO DUMP
ANYTHING ELSE?

01:41.250 --> 01:43.500
NAH, I'M GOOD.
I'M GONNA HEAD UPSTAIRS.

01:43.500 --> 01:45.208
OKAY.

01:52.834 --> 01:54.291
TIM, ARE YOU OKAY?

02:01.166 --> 02:02.583
TIM?

02:12.291 --> 02:14.125
TIM!

02:17.291 --> 02:19.917
HEY, QUIT SCREWING AROUND!

02:21.291 --> 02:23.959
HEY. HEY, WHAT HAPPENED?

02:27.542 --> 02:29.417
BRANDON SMIT, 22,

02:29.417 --> 02:31.417
A SENIOR
AT HALLRIDGE UNIVERSITY,

02:31.417 --> 02:33.125
AND HIS BROTHER, TIMOTHY, 18,

02:33.125 --> 02:35.792
A FRESHMAN AT
BURLINGTON CREST COLLEGE.

02:35.792 --> 02:38.041
BOTH BOYS HAIL
FROM ROSWELL, GEORGIA.

02:38.041 --> 02:41.250
THEY WERE ON A BREAK VISITING
JOHANNESBURG, SOUTH AFRICA,

02:41.250 --> 02:43.709
WHERE THEY'D TAKEN
TEMPORARY JOBS IN A BAR

02:43.709 --> 02:45.875
WORKING FOR THEIR AUNT,
MARIAM NELL,

02:45.875 --> 02:48.250
WHO REPORTED THEM MISSING
24 HOURS AGO.

02:48.250 --> 02:49.834
Then eight hours ago,

02:49.834 --> 02:52.083
police discovered the body
of Timothy Smit,

02:52.083 --> 02:54.333
mutilated and staged
in an abandoned shanty

02:54.333 --> 02:56.125
just inside
the Azaria district,

02:56.125 --> 02:57.625
one of the poorest
neighborhoods in Johannesburg

02:57.625 --> 02:59.834
and 12 miles
from their aunt's bar.

02:59.834 --> 03:02.667
BRANDON'S STILL MISSING,
AND IT WOULD APPEAR

03:02.667 --> 03:05.333
THAT HIS MURDER IS CONSISTENT
WITH THIS.

03:05.333 --> 03:07.750
ONE MONTH AGO, LARA BOSCH, 29,

03:07.750 --> 03:10.083
WAS KIDNAPPED
FROM HER HOME IN PRETORIA,

03:10.083 --> 03:12.542
40 MINUTES NORTH
OF JOHANNESBURG.

03:12.542 --> 03:16.166
HER BODY WAS LATER FOUND
LIKE THIS, ALSO INSIDE AZARIA.

03:16.166 --> 03:18.208
YOU KNOW, THE DESECRATION
OF THESE BODIES,

03:18.208 --> 03:20.000
IT'S VERY SPECIFIC.

03:20.000 --> 03:23.500
BODIES CAKED IN WHITE CLAY,
SPIKES DRIVEN THROUGH FOREHEADS,

03:23.500 --> 03:25.333
TONGUES SEVERED.

03:25.333 --> 03:26.750
IT'S DERIVED FROM

03:26.750 --> 03:28.667
A RARE SOUTHERN AFRICAN
DIVINING PRACTICE,

03:28.667 --> 03:30.959
WHICH IS MEANT TO REPRESENT
UMKOVU,

03:30.959 --> 03:32.709
WHICH ARE BASICALLY

03:32.709 --> 03:34.542
CORPSES THAT HAVE BEEN DUG UP
AND REVIVED BY A SHAMAN

03:34.542 --> 03:36.083
IN ORDER TO DO HIS BIDDING.

03:36.083 --> 03:38.041
SO YOU THINK OUR UNSUB BELIEVES
THAT HE'S RECRUITING

03:38.041 --> 03:39.792
HIS OWN ZOMBIE SOUL BRIGADE?

03:39.792 --> 03:43.208
NOW GIVEN THE PRESENT STATUS
OF BRANDON SMIT'S ABDUCTION,

03:43.208 --> 03:45.250
THE SOUTH AFRICAN
SPECIAL FORCES BRIGADE

03:45.250 --> 03:47.041
HAVE TAKEN CHARGE
OF THE MISSION.

03:47.041 --> 03:48.875
PARAMILITARY TACTICS
ARE A BIT OF A BLUNT INSTRUMENT,

03:48.875 --> 03:50.083
DON'T YOU THINK?

03:50.083 --> 03:51.542
THAT MIGHT BE WHY
OUR AMBASSADOR

03:51.542 --> 03:53.125
AND THE SOUTH AFRICAN
FOREIGN MINISTER

03:53.125 --> 03:55.375
HAVE ASKED US TO WORK
WITH THE S.F.B.

03:55.375 --> 03:57.125
WELL, TIME IS NOT
ON OUR SIDE.

03:57.125 --> 03:59.291
BRANDON'S BEEN MISSING
FOR OVER 36 HOURS NOW.

03:59.291 --> 04:01.083
I MEAN, BY THE BOOK,
AFTER 72,

04:01.083 --> 04:04.000
A RESCUE MISSION USUALLY TURNS
INTO A RECOVERY MISSION.

04:04.000 --> 04:05.959
YEAH, BUT IF OUR UNSUB PLANNED
ON KILLING BOTH BROTHERS,

04:05.959 --> 04:07.750
WHY WOULDN'T HE HAVE
JUST DONE IT AT THE SAME TIME

04:07.750 --> 04:10.083
AND THEN ARRANGE THEIR BODIES
SIDE BY SIDE?

04:10.083 --> 04:12.500
BECAUSE, FOR WHATEVER REASON,

04:12.500 --> 04:15.917
OUR UNSUB'S NOT DONE
WITH BRANDON...YET.

04:15.917 --> 04:18.291
AS TERRIBLE AS THAT SOUNDS,

04:18.291 --> 04:21.458
IT MAY MEAN WE STILL HAVE TIME
TO SAVE HIM.

04:37.875 --> 04:39.250
WHERE'S MY BROTHER?

04:42.250 --> 04:44.583
HEY! WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH HIM?!

04:50.458 --> 04:54.333
WENA UNGUFAKAZI WAMI.

04:54.333 --> 04:58.208
WENA UNGUFAKAZI WAMI.

04:58.208 --> 05:02.500
WHAT?
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

05:02.500 --> 05:03.959
PLEASE!

05:03.959 --> 05:05.291
NO!

05:05.291 --> 05:08.458
♪♪

05:29.458 --> 05:34.500
Jack: A ZULU PROVERB REMINDS US,
"HOPE DOES NOT KILL."

05:40.041 --> 05:41.375
Man: YES, WE'LL TAKE CARE
OF IT.

05:41.375 --> 05:42.792
WELCOME TO YOU.

05:42.792 --> 05:45.500
I AM
BRIGADIER GENERAL YAZEEN ZWANE.

05:45.500 --> 05:47.834
YOU MUST BE
UNIT CHIEF JACK GARRETT, EH?

05:47.834 --> 05:49.375
YES, I AM,

05:49.375 --> 05:52.208
AND THIS IS MY TEAM,
SUPERVISORY SPECIAL AGENTS

05:52.208 --> 05:54.583
CLARA SEGER,
MATT SIMMONS, AND MAE JARVIS.

05:54.583 --> 05:56.875
IF YOU WOULD,
FOLLOW ME, PLEASE.

05:56.875 --> 05:59.041
I HAVE BEEN
IN CONSTANT COMMUNICATION

05:59.041 --> 06:01.875
WITH YOUR AMBASSADOR,
AS WELL AS OUR FOREIGN MINISTER,

06:01.875 --> 06:05.166
AND I ASSURE YOU
OF THE UTMOST COOPERATION

06:05.166 --> 06:07.125
WITH THIS MISSION.
I APPRECIATE THAT, GENERAL.

06:07.125 --> 06:08.834
HOWEVER, WE ARE CONCERNED

06:08.834 --> 06:11.500
ABOUT THE APPLICATION
OF COUNTERINSURGENCY TACTICS

06:11.500 --> 06:14.000
IN THIS INVESTIGATION.
I UNDERSTAND.

06:14.000 --> 06:17.875
I SUPPOSE IT SEEMED LIKE, UH,
USING A CANNON TO SWAT A FLY.

06:17.875 --> 06:19.667
OBVIOUSLY, WE'D FEEL
MORE COMFORTABLE

06:19.667 --> 06:20.959
COORDINATING THIS MISSION

06:20.959 --> 06:22.834
BASED ON A COMPREHENSIVE
CRIMINAL PROFILE.

06:22.834 --> 06:25.458
WE REALLY NEED TO GET TO WORK
ON THAT IMMEDIATELY.

06:25.458 --> 06:27.875
BRANDON'S LIFE DEPENDS ON IT.
I COULD NOT AGREE WITH YOU MORE.

06:27.875 --> 06:30.875
THAT IS WHY WE'VE CALLED IN
OUR COUNTRY'S PREMIER PROFILER

06:30.875 --> 06:32.667
TO ASSIST YOU --

06:32.667 --> 06:36.208
LIEUTENANT ANANDA DOSHI.

06:36.208 --> 06:39.792
I AM SORRY. WILL THERE BE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

06:39.792 --> 06:42.959
NO. NO PROBLEM.

06:42.959 --> 06:44.834
BUT I'LL WANNA WALK THROUGH
THE BODY DUMP SITE

06:44.834 --> 06:46.542
WITH AGENT SEGER,

06:46.542 --> 06:49.291
AND HAVE AGENT SIMMONS HERE
INSPECT THE ABDUCTION SITE

06:49.291 --> 06:53.125
WHILE AGENT JARVIS ASSISTS
WITH TIMOTHY SMIT'S AUTOPSY.
CERTAINLY.

06:53.125 --> 06:54.834
I WILL ARRANGE FOR YOUR ESCORT

06:54.834 --> 06:57.041
AND FOR LIEUTENANT DOSHI
TO MEET YOU

06:57.041 --> 06:58.542
AT THE AZARIA SCENE.

06:58.542 --> 07:00.250
YOU SURE
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY

07:00.250 --> 07:02.417
WORKING WITH HER AGAIN?
I'M SURE.

07:02.417 --> 07:03.750
IS THIS THE SAME ANANDA DOSHI

07:03.750 --> 07:05.917
THAT'S RESPONSIBLE
FOR CATCHING GABRIEL IMANI,

07:05.917 --> 07:08.000
A.K.A. "THE ARCHANGEL,"
IN MADAGASCAR?

07:08.000 --> 07:09.375
DIDN'T YOU WORK THAT CASE,
BOSS?

07:09.375 --> 07:11.834
YEAH, WHICH IS WHY
I'M BRINGING IT UP.

07:11.834 --> 07:13.875
LOOK, IF THEY WANT HER,
WE GOT HER.

07:13.875 --> 07:15.417
WE HAVE A JOB TO DO.

07:16.875 --> 07:20.083
WHY DID I ALLOW MY SONS TO GO?

07:20.083 --> 07:23.041
I INSISTED YOU LET THEM, ARMAND.

07:23.041 --> 07:25.875
IT'S NOT LIKE
THEY HADN'T BEEN THERE BEFORE.

07:25.875 --> 07:28.667
THEY MISSED YOUR SISTER.

07:28.667 --> 07:31.417
THEN SHE SHOULD HAVE COME
TO VISIT US.

07:31.417 --> 07:34.250
I'LL STILL NEVER UNDERSTAND
WHY SHE CHOSE TO STAY

07:34.250 --> 07:36.917
IN THAT GODFORSAKEN PLACE
AFTER I LEFT.

07:36.917 --> 07:39.792
MR. AND MRS. SMIT, I KNOW
THIS A DIFFICULT TIME FOR YOU,

07:39.792 --> 07:41.959
BUT YOU CANNOT BLAME YOURSELVES

07:41.959 --> 07:43.875
FOR WHAT HAPPENED
TO TIMOTHY AND BRANDON.

07:43.875 --> 07:45.792
I WISH I COULD BELIEVE YOU,

07:45.792 --> 07:47.792
BUT A MAN'S
SOLE RESPONSIBILITY

07:47.792 --> 07:49.792
IS TO PROTECT
THE ONES HE LOVES.

07:49.792 --> 07:52.750
THAT'S WHY I LEFT SOUTH AFRICA
25 YEARS AGO.

07:52.750 --> 07:54.083
I MET MY WIFE.

07:54.083 --> 07:56.959
I WANTED TO START A FAMILY
IN A BETTER PLACE.

07:56.959 --> 07:59.875
I UNDERSTAND, SIR.
I'M -- I'M SORRY.

07:59.875 --> 08:01.667
I JUST HAVE
A COUPLE MORE QUESTIONS.

08:01.667 --> 08:03.125
GIVEN THE NEIGHBORHOOD,

08:03.125 --> 08:04.792
DID THE BOYS EVER MENTION

08:04.792 --> 08:07.625
BEING HASSLED
BY ANY OF THE LOCAL GANGS?

08:07.625 --> 08:09.625
NO. WHY?

08:09.625 --> 08:11.041
NOTHING SPECIFIC.

08:11.041 --> 08:14.041
WE JUST HAVE TO EVALUATE
EVERY POSSIBLE THREAT.

08:14.041 --> 08:17.625
NOW, MR. SMIT, YOU IMMIGRATED
FROM SOUTH AFRICA IN 1990

08:17.625 --> 08:19.792
AND THEN BECAME A U.S. CITIZEN
IN 2004?

08:19.792 --> 08:21.500
THAT'S CORRECT.

08:21.500 --> 08:24.083
AND YOUR ONLY OTHER
LIVING RELATIVE IN SOUTH AFRICA

08:24.083 --> 08:25.667
IS YOUR SISTER, MARIAM NELL?

08:25.667 --> 08:28.333
IS THAT RIGHT?
YES.

08:28.333 --> 08:30.667
THE BOYS JUST ADORED MARIAM.

08:30.667 --> 08:34.208
SHE AND I WERE THE ONES WHO MADE
THE ARRANGEMENTS FOR THEM

08:34.208 --> 08:36.750
TO STAY AND WORK DOWN THERE
FOR A FEW WEEKS.

08:36.750 --> 08:38.917
THE ONLY SECURITY CAMERA
THE POLICE FOUND

08:38.917 --> 08:41.583
WAS SITUATED OVER THIS BAR
POINTING AT THE CASH REGISTER.

08:41.583 --> 08:45.250
YEAH. THE ONLY ONE
I THOUGHT I NEEDED.

08:45.250 --> 08:48.166
THAT, AND THE GEWEER
BEHIND THE BAR.

08:48.166 --> 08:49.500
SORRY. THE -- THE WHAT?

08:49.500 --> 08:51.834
I BOUGHT A GUN. A .38.

08:51.834 --> 08:55.166
RIGHT, BUT NO GUN WAS --
WAS FOUND.

08:55.166 --> 08:58.250
IT WASN'T ANY HELP AT ALL,
WAS IT?

08:58.250 --> 09:00.458
I JUST NEVER SHOULD HAVE
LEFT THEM.

09:00.458 --> 09:03.750
MS. NELL, DID YOU OR THE BOYS
EVER RECEIVE ANY THREATS?

09:03.750 --> 09:05.750
JA.

09:05.750 --> 09:09.041
A COUPLE OF IBHULOHO CAME AROUND
A FEW MONTHS BACK.

09:09.041 --> 09:11.041
THEY WANTED ME TO START
PAYING THEM PROTECTION MONEY,

09:11.041 --> 09:14.208
BUT I REFUSED TO PAY THEM.

09:14.208 --> 09:16.166
YOU THINK THEY DID THIS
TO MY NEPHEWS?

09:16.166 --> 09:18.000
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD
IDENTIFY THESE MEN?

09:18.000 --> 09:19.375
JA, I MIGHT.

09:19.375 --> 09:22.542
UH, JUST ONE LAST THING.

09:22.542 --> 09:24.834
YOU RECOGNIZE THIS WOMAN?
NO.

09:24.834 --> 09:27.166
Monty:
HER NAME IS LARA BOSCH.

09:27.166 --> 09:28.750
BOSCH?

09:28.750 --> 09:31.750
YES. DOES THAT
RING A BELL?

09:31.750 --> 09:34.792
NO, I'M SORRY.

09:36.667 --> 09:39.750
YOU THINK SHE'S INVOLVED
SOMEHOW?

09:39.750 --> 09:43.542
SHE'S ANOTHER VICTIM, MA'AM.

09:43.542 --> 09:47.792
♪♪

10:00.792 --> 10:02.333
Clara: YEAH, I'VE HEARD
DOSHI'S METHODOLOGY

10:02.333 --> 10:03.667
CAN BE A LITTLE UNORTHODOX,

10:03.667 --> 10:05.125
BUT YOU NEVER TOLD ME WHAT
HAPPENED BETWEEN THE TWO OF YOU.

10:05.125 --> 10:06.792
WHAT CAUSED THE FALLING OUT?

10:06.792 --> 10:08.792
I'M NOT SURE
THIS IS THE TIME.

10:08.792 --> 10:12.000
I'M NOT SURE IT'S FAIR TO HAVE
ME GO IN THERE FLYING BLIND.

10:12.000 --> 10:13.625
DOSHI MAY HAVE BEEN TRAINED
BY SCOTLAND YARD

10:13.625 --> 10:15.125
IN FORENSIC PSYCHOLOGY,

10:15.125 --> 10:17.917
BUT SHE DOESN'T REALLY
SEE HERSELF AS A PROFILER.

10:17.917 --> 10:20.500
THEN HOW DOES SHE SEE HERSELF?

10:20.500 --> 10:22.959
UNGESABI.

10:22.959 --> 10:25.208
NGIZWE.

10:25.208 --> 10:27.917
WENA AKUDINGEKI WESABE.

10:27.917 --> 10:32.583
TIMOTHY, SPEAK, IF YOU WILL.

10:37.083 --> 10:38.917
IT'S BEEN TOO LONG, JACK.

10:38.917 --> 10:40.375
I'M TOLD YOU NOW RUN

10:40.375 --> 10:43.250
YOUR OWN PERSONAL DIVISION
OF THE FBI.

10:43.250 --> 10:44.917
IT'S NOT MY PERSONAL DIVISION.

10:44.917 --> 10:47.458
IT'S THE BUREAU'S
INTERNATIONAL RESPONSE TEAM.

10:47.458 --> 10:49.000
I'M THE UNIT CHIEF.

10:49.000 --> 10:51.250
AND THIS IS
S.S.A. CLARA SEGER.

10:51.250 --> 10:53.709
LIEUTENANT DOSHI,
YOUR REPUTATION PRECEDES YOU.

10:53.709 --> 10:56.792
I'M AFRAID
THAT'S MY CROSS TO BEAR.

10:56.792 --> 10:58.750
THE CANDLES?
I'M SURE YOU WAITED --

10:58.750 --> 11:01.500
UNTIL THE SCENE
WAS PROCESSED. YES, I DID.

11:01.500 --> 11:05.834
UNFORTUNATELY, THE TIME ELAPSED
WAS FAR TOO LONG.

11:05.834 --> 11:08.625
IF TIMOTHY FOUND HIS WAY
BACK HERE,

11:08.625 --> 11:10.625
HE DID NOT LINGER FOR LONG.

11:10.625 --> 11:12.125
YOU MEAN TIMOTHY'S SPIRIT?

11:12.125 --> 11:14.500
NO. I MEAN TIMOTHY HIMSELF.

11:14.500 --> 11:17.125
I DO NOT SUBSCRIBE
TO THE WESTERN DUALISM

11:17.125 --> 11:18.875
OF PHYSICAL VERSUS SPIRITUAL.

11:18.875 --> 11:22.166
WHEN WE DIE, THERE'S NOT SOME
PART OF US THAT LIVES ON.

11:22.166 --> 11:25.000
IT'S THE WHOLE OF US
THAT EVOLVES

11:25.000 --> 11:28.333
INTO A NEW AND MARVELOUS
INCARNATION.

11:28.333 --> 11:31.875
UH, IF THAT IS TRUE, THEN WHY
WOULD TIMOTHY COME BACK HERE?

11:31.875 --> 11:34.333
BECAUSE THE REAL TRAGEDY
OF MURDER

11:34.333 --> 11:38.709
IS THAT OUR TRANSMIGRATION
IS SO ABRUPT THAT WE GET SCARED

11:38.709 --> 11:41.834
AND TRY TO CLING
TO THIS FLESH AND BONE,

11:41.834 --> 11:45.500
THUS A HOMICIDE VICTIM
LINGERS AT HIS CRIME SCENE.

11:45.500 --> 11:48.291
WELL, BASED ON
THE LACK OF BLOOD EVIDENCE,

11:48.291 --> 11:50.709
MAYBE TIMOTHY DIDN'T
COME BACK HERE

11:50.709 --> 11:53.875
BECAUSE THIS WASN'T WHERE
HE WAS MURDERED AND MUTILATED.

11:53.875 --> 11:55.834
MM.
JUST WHERE HE WAS STAGED.

11:55.834 --> 11:58.875
YEAH, STAGED IN CLOSE PROXIMITY
OF WHERE LARA'S BODY WAS,

11:58.875 --> 12:00.250
JUST A QUARTER-MILE AWAY.

12:00.250 --> 12:01.709
THIS AZARIA DISTRICT --

12:01.709 --> 12:03.792
IT APPEARS TO MEAN SOMETHING
TO OUR UNSUB.

12:03.792 --> 12:08.542
BUT HE'S A POACHER. HE LIKES
TO HUNT ACROSS A WIDE TERRAIN.

12:08.542 --> 12:10.250
VICTORIA TO JOHANNESBURG --

12:10.250 --> 12:12.458
THAT'S NEARLY
9,000 SQUARE KILOMETERS.

12:12.458 --> 12:15.166
WHICH ISN'T INCONSISTENT
WITH OUR GANG THEORY.

12:15.166 --> 12:17.375
BUT THE EXPLICIT PRECISION
OF MUTILATIONS,

12:17.375 --> 12:19.625
IT SEEMS MORE LIKELY TO BE
A PHYSICAL MANIFESTATION

12:19.625 --> 12:23.250
OF OUR UNSUB'S
INTERNAL FANTASY PSYCHOSIS.

12:23.250 --> 12:24.750
YOU THINK SO?

12:24.750 --> 12:26.917
'CAUSE I THINK THEY LOOK
LIKE VERY CONVINCING

12:26.917 --> 12:30.125
"DON'T YOU DARE MESS WITH ME"
WARNINGS.

12:30.125 --> 12:33.583
AGAIN, NOT INCONSISTENT
WITH THE GANG.

12:33.583 --> 12:35.709
THE ONLY QUESTION IS, TO WHOM
ARE THESE WARNINGS DIRECTED?

12:35.709 --> 12:38.000
STILL, WHY GO
TO ALL THIS TROUBLE?

12:38.000 --> 12:40.917
IF THESE ARE FEAR TACTICS,
THEY SEEM EXTREME.

12:40.917 --> 12:42.458
THIS IS SOUTH AFRICA, JACK.

12:42.458 --> 12:44.792
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH
SOME SERIOUS STRIFE.

12:44.792 --> 12:47.750
IF YOU REALLY WANT TO PUT
THE FEAR OF GOD INTO US,

12:47.750 --> 12:50.291
YOU DEFINITELY NEED
TO STEP UP YOUR GAME.

13:05.083 --> 13:06.375
UHH!

13:10.417 --> 13:13.291
IGAZI.

13:13.291 --> 13:17.208
WENA UNGUFAKAZI WAMI.

13:17.208 --> 13:19.750
IQINISO.

13:21.709 --> 13:23.709
MARIAM NELL'S PHYSICAL
DESCRIPTION OF THE GANG MEMBERS

