26:21.333 --> 26:22.834
THAT'S WHERE
THIS COMES FROM.

26:22.834 --> 26:24.875
YES, THE TRUTH
AND RECONCILIATION COMMISSION

26:24.875 --> 26:28.333
WAS SET UP AS AN OPEN FORUM FOR
PEOPLE TO CONFESS THEIR CRIMES

26:28.333 --> 26:29.917
WITHOUT FEAR OF PROSECUTION.

26:29.917 --> 26:32.667
AND IN THE NAME
OF NATIONAL RECONCILIATION,

26:32.667 --> 26:36.291
THE NAMES OF THE THREE PRETORIUS
AGENTS WERE NEVER DISCLOSED,

26:36.291 --> 26:40.041
THEIR CRIMES AGAINST HUMANITY
NEVER TO BE PUNISHED.

26:40.041 --> 26:43.458
AND SO IT WOULD SEEM THAT LIKE
MY FELLOW SOUTH AFRICANS,

26:43.458 --> 26:47.750
I'VE NOT ONLY TRIED TO FORGIVE,
APPARENTLY I NEARLY FORGOT.

26:47.750 --> 26:49.083
AND NOW YEARS LATER,

26:49.083 --> 26:51.750
OUR UNSUB MIMICS
THIS PARTICULAR MURDER.

26:51.750 --> 26:54.583
BECAUSE MAYBE HE'S IDENTIFIED
THESE THREE MEN

26:54.583 --> 26:57.709
AND IS NOW TARGETING
THEIR CHILDREN FOR REVENGE.

26:57.709 --> 27:00.583
THE CRUELEST PUNISHMENT OF ALL
IS FOR A PARENT TO BURY A CHILD.

27:00.583 --> 27:02.875
IN THIS CASE, CHILD BY BLOOD,
IF WE BELIEVE

27:02.875 --> 27:04.625
THAT HE'S KEEPING
BRANDON ALIVE.

27:04.625 --> 27:06.083
OKAY, NOT TO BE
THE NAYSAYER HERE,

27:06.083 --> 27:07.834
BUT ACCUSING ROWAN BOSCH
AND ARMAND SMIT

27:07.834 --> 27:09.959
OF BEING PART OF THIS GROUP
IS A PRETTY SERIOUS THING.

27:09.959 --> 27:11.959
I WOULD FEEL A LOT MORE
COMFORTABLE IF WE HAD

27:11.959 --> 27:14.166
MORE TO GO ON
THAN JUST A THEORY.
I'LL HAVE MONTY FOLLOW UP

27:14.166 --> 27:16.000
WITH THE COVERT HISTORY
ON BOSCH AND SMIT.

27:16.000 --> 27:19.792
WE MIGHT FIND SOMETHING IN ONE
OF OUR OWN INTELLIGENCE FILES.

27:19.792 --> 27:21.291
YOU KNOW, WITH THIS LATEST
CRIME SCENE,

27:21.291 --> 27:22.583
I THINK WE MIGHT HAVE
ENOUGH DATA

27:22.583 --> 27:23.792
FOR SIMMONS AND I
TO HEAD BACK TO THE JET

27:23.792 --> 27:25.291
AND BUILD A GEO-PROFILE.

27:25.291 --> 27:27.959
AND AGENT JARVIS AND I CAN
RUN OUR CRIMINAL PROFILE

27:27.959 --> 27:30.250
AGAINST A NEW POOL
OF POTENTIAL SUSPECTS --

27:30.250 --> 27:33.625
THE SURVIVING FAMILY MEMBERS
OF PRETORIUS' VICTIMS.

27:33.625 --> 27:35.667
OKAY, LET'S GET TO WORK.

27:35.667 --> 27:38.667
♪♪

27:47.458 --> 27:51.291
MR. SMIT, I HAVE SOMETHING
I NEED TO SHOW YOU.

27:52.333 --> 27:53.959
YOU RECOGNIZE THIS MAN?

27:55.500 --> 27:57.291
SORRY, I DON'T KNOW HIM.
OKAY.

27:57.291 --> 27:59.458
WELL, YOU CAN CLEAR UP
ONE MORE DISCREPANCY FOR ME.

27:59.458 --> 28:01.667
THIS MAN'S NAME IS
ROWAN BOSCH.

28:01.667 --> 28:03.625
YOU TWO HAVE SOMETHING
VERY INTERESTING IN COMMON.

28:03.625 --> 28:05.208
NEITHER ONE OF YOU
IS ON RECORD AS SERVING

28:05.208 --> 28:06.750
IN THE SOUTH AFRICAN
DEFENSE FORCE.

28:06.750 --> 28:08.333
WHAT'S INTERESTING ABOUT THAT

28:08.333 --> 28:09.917
IS THAT MILITARY SERVICE
WAS COMPULSORY

28:09.917 --> 28:12.291
FOR ALL WHITE MALES
UNTIL 1993.

28:12.291 --> 28:14.166
WHAT ARE YOU INSINUATING,
SON?

28:14.166 --> 28:18.083
THAT'D BE "AGENT MONTGOMERY,"
SIR.

28:19.291 --> 28:21.208
WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE
THAT TIMOTHY WAS MURDERED

28:21.208 --> 28:25.125
AND BRANDON WAS TAKEN
AS PAYBACK FOR PRETORIUS.

28:29.208 --> 28:32.458
YOU WERE ONE OF THEM,
WEREN'T YOU?

28:32.458 --> 28:35.709
HOW DARE YOU ACCUSE ME
OF THAT?

28:35.709 --> 28:37.959
WHAT IN GOD'S NAME
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

28:37.959 --> 28:41.375
WHAT ABOUT MY SON?
WHERE IS HE?

28:41.375 --> 28:43.041
I SWEAR, IF HE DIES,

28:43.041 --> 28:45.542
I WILL HOLD YOU
PERSONALLY RESPONSIBLE,

28:45.542 --> 28:48.291
AGENT MONTGOMERY.

28:51.625 --> 28:53.458
I'M SORRY, JACK.

28:53.458 --> 28:55.417
I SHOULDN'T HAVE
CONFRONTED HIM LIKE THAT.

28:55.417 --> 28:57.625
JUST WHEN I COMPARED
THE TWO BIOS,

28:57.625 --> 28:59.875
I realized I had seen
the pattern of detail,

28:59.875 --> 29:01.375
or lack thereof, before,

29:01.375 --> 29:03.375
IN COVER STORIES
CREATED FOR WITNESS PROTECTION.

29:03.375 --> 29:05.709
Then he had the nerve to look me
in the eye and lie.

29:05.709 --> 29:08.041
BUT HIS DEFLECTION
CONFIRMS OUR THEORY.

29:08.041 --> 29:10.333
He and Bosch are two of
the three agents of Pretorius.

29:10.333 --> 29:13.250
AND NOW WE'RE FACE-TO-FACE
WITH ONE OF THE MEN RESPONSIBLE

29:13.250 --> 29:15.750
FOR TORTURING AND MURDERING
14 INNOCENT PEOPLE --

29:15.750 --> 29:17.166
PEOPLE WHO WERE JUST FIGHTING
FOR THEIR FREEDOM,

29:17.166 --> 29:18.417
AND THERE'S NOT A DAMN THING
WE CAN DO

29:18.417 --> 29:19.875
TO BRING THEM TO JUSTICE.

29:19.875 --> 29:21.583
I KNOW, BUT I THINK
THE BEST THING RIGHT NOW

29:21.583 --> 29:23.166
IS TO REMEMBER
THE SINS OF THE FATHER

29:23.166 --> 29:24.709
HAVE NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE SON.

29:24.709 --> 29:27.166
We need to stay focused
on saving Brandon's life.

29:27.166 --> 29:28.917
YOU'RE RIGHT.

29:30.875 --> 29:32.542
HOW'S IT LOOKING?

29:32.542 --> 29:34.750
OH, WELL, THE BIGGEST CHALLENGE
HAS BEEN RECONCILING

29:34.750 --> 29:36.834
THE TWO AXIOMS
OF SERIAL KILLER BEHAVIOR.

29:36.834 --> 29:38.875
RIGHT -- NEVER COMMIT A CRIME
TOO CLOSE TO HOME,

29:38.875 --> 29:40.750
AND NEVER TRAVEL FURTHER
THAN NECESSARY

29:40.750 --> 29:43.000
TO GET YOUR VICTIMS.
BUT OUR UNSUB IS A POACHER.

29:43.000 --> 29:44.667
HE'S WILLING TO GO
THE EXTRA MILE.

29:44.667 --> 29:47.041
WHICH COMPLICATES THE MATH
FOR OUR MODEL.

29:47.041 --> 29:48.667
BUT MONTY HOOKED US UP
WITH THIS PROGRAM

29:48.667 --> 29:50.583
THAT HELPS US COMPARE
THE PATTERNS OF OUR UNSUB

29:50.583 --> 29:52.208
WITH THE PATTERNS
OF PAST SERIAL KILLERS

29:52.208 --> 29:54.625
ACTIVE IN SIMILAR URBAN TERRAIN.

29:54.625 --> 29:57.875
SO...IT SHOULD BE ABLE
TO CALCULATE

29:57.875 --> 30:00.959
THE HIGHEST PROBABLE LOCATION
OF OUR UNSUB'S HOME, SWEET HOME.

30:00.959 --> 30:02.709
NICE WORK.

30:02.709 --> 30:05.458
LOOKS LIKE OUR UNSUB MAY BE
SOMEWHERE IN BRIARS POINT.

30:05.458 --> 30:07.792
YEAH, BUT BY HOME, WE'RE
PROBABLY NOT TALKING

30:07.792 --> 30:10.083
ABOUT HIS RESIDENCE.
THIS GUY WANTS ISOLATION.

30:10.083 --> 30:14.125
SO HE MIGHT JUST LIKE THIS OLD
NORRIS MINING INDUSTRIES PLANT

30:14.125 --> 30:15.625
WHICH CLOSED IN 1975.

30:15.625 --> 30:17.625
CLARA, YOU COORDINATE
FROM THE COMMAND POST.

30:17.625 --> 30:20.875
SIMMONS AND I WILL ROUND UP
GENERAL ZWANE AND HIS MEN.

30:20.875 --> 30:24.625
♪♪

30:51.417 --> 30:53.083
BRANDON.
LET ME GO.
PLEASE.

30:53.083 --> 30:54.417
BRANDON.
WHAT?

30:54.417 --> 30:56.667
HEY. YOU'RE GONNA BE
ALL RIGHT, SON.

30:56.667 --> 30:59.709
I'M JACK GARRETT, FBI.
YOU'RE SAFE.

30:59.709 --> 31:03.417
♪♪

31:05.750 --> 31:07.667
FBI! DON'T MOVE!

31:07.667 --> 31:09.500
DROP YOUR WEAPON!

31:09.500 --> 31:11.041
Man: DROP IT!

31:11.041 --> 31:13.208
BEKA PHANSI ISIBHAMU!

31:19.917 --> 31:22.709
DO NOT MOVE! I WILL SHOOT!

31:23.959 --> 31:25.875
HIS ARM'S TIED
TO THE CHAIR.

31:31.875 --> 31:35.375
♪♪

31:44.041 --> 31:45.750
OH, MY GOD.

31:45.750 --> 31:47.291
IT'S ROWAN BOSCH.

31:49.417 --> 31:51.875
SON OF A BITCH
LOBOTOMIZED HIM.

31:56.625 --> 31:58.375
THANKS.

31:58.375 --> 31:59.750
SO BOSCH IS
IN CRITICAL CONDITION.

31:59.750 --> 32:01.291
BRANDON APPEARS TO BE
STABLE.

32:01.291 --> 32:02.709
THEY'RE BOTH ON THEIR WAY
TO THE HOSPITAL NOW.

32:02.709 --> 32:04.375
WELL, THAT'S GOOD NEWS.
YEAH.

32:04.375 --> 32:05.667
BAD NEWS IS,
OUR UNSUB STAGED THE SCENE

32:05.667 --> 32:07.166
LIKE HE KNEW WE WERE COMING.

32:07.166 --> 32:09.583
Or he knew this was
his end game.

32:09.583 --> 32:12.375
MAYBE OUR BEAST
IS ON HIS FINAL HUNT.

32:12.375 --> 32:14.083
WHERE ARE WE IN RUNNING
THE PROFILE

32:14.083 --> 32:15.417
AGAINST
OUR VICTIMS' FAMILIES?

32:15.417 --> 32:16.875
NOWHERE IS WHERE WE ARE.

32:16.875 --> 32:18.583
THERE'S NOT ONE VIABLE SUSPECT
IN THE POOL.

32:18.583 --> 32:21.458
AND THERE'S STILL ONE MORE AGENT
OF PRETORIUS TO IDENTIFY.

32:21.458 --> 32:23.000
EVEN IF HE IS DEAD,

32:23.000 --> 32:24.542
HIS CHILDREN OR BLOOD RELATIVES
ARE IN DANGER.

32:24.542 --> 32:27.125
- THERE'S SOMETHING WE'RE MISSING.
- About what?

32:27.125 --> 32:29.583
THE VICTIMS? PRETORIUS?
I'M NOT SURE, BUT I DON'T THINK

32:29.583 --> 32:31.041
WE'RE LOOKING AT THIS
THE RIGHT WAY.

32:31.041 --> 32:33.041
I MEAN, IT WAS THE LAST GASP
OF APARTHEID.

32:33.041 --> 32:34.625
Even President Botha

32:34.625 --> 32:35.917
was willing to negotiate
with Mandela for peace.

32:35.917 --> 32:37.375
SOMETHING HAD TO BE DONE,

32:37.375 --> 32:39.542
ESPECIALLY IN THIS
SECURITY STATE WHERE...

32:41.709 --> 32:43.417
WHERE WHITE IS BLACK,

32:43.417 --> 32:45.959
AND BLACK IS WHITE.

32:50.834 --> 32:53.041
OKAY, THERE WAS A MAN NAMED
DAVID LUBBE.

32:53.041 --> 32:54.625
HE WAS ARRESTED AND CONFESSED

32:54.625 --> 32:56.750
to killing Miller.
He died in prison.

32:56.750 --> 32:58.458
MONTY?

32:58.458 --> 33:00.458
Clara, what if the murder
of Constable Miller

33:00.458 --> 33:01.750
was a false flag?

33:01.750 --> 33:03.500
WHAT IF IT HAD BEEN
THIS COVERT OP

33:03.500 --> 33:06.166
THAT WAS DESIGNED TO INCITE
THE SOCIAL UNREST NECESSARY

33:06.166 --> 33:08.125
TO JUSTIFY
THE CREATION OF PRETORIUS?

33:08.125 --> 33:09.583
WELL, IF THAT'S TRUE...

33:09.583 --> 33:11.000
WELL, THEN WE NEED TO APPLY
OUR PROFILE

33:11.000 --> 33:12.583
TO THE FAMILY
OF SARA MILLER.

33:16.333 --> 33:18.458
DO YOU REMEMBER
CONSTABLE MILLER?

33:18.458 --> 33:20.291
YOU REMEMBER WHAT YOU
AND YOUR PRETORIUS BOYS

33:20.291 --> 33:22.667
DID TO MY SISTER?

33:22.667 --> 33:24.291
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

33:24.291 --> 33:25.667
YOU HAVE THE WRONG MAN!

33:27.041 --> 33:28.625
THE WRONG MAN WENT TO PRISON.

33:28.625 --> 33:31.500
AND HE DIED THERE.

33:31.500 --> 33:33.500
ROWAN BOSCH
TOLD ME EVERYTHING.

33:33.500 --> 33:36.792
HE CAME TO ME, DYING OF CANCER,
ASKING FOR FORGIVENESS.

33:36.792 --> 33:39.709
EVEN HAD DOCUMENTS TO PROVE
EVERY WORD.

33:39.709 --> 33:42.333
PLEASE. THERE MUST BE
SOMETHING THAT I COULD --

33:42.333 --> 33:44.333
YOU COULD DO?
YES.

33:44.333 --> 33:47.458
HMM. YOU CAN WAIT WITH ME
FOR YOUR LITTLE GIRL LYDIA

33:47.458 --> 33:50.041
TO COME HOME, AND YOU CAN WATCH
AS I SPILL HER BLOOD

33:50.041 --> 33:51.500
ALL OVER THIS FLOOR.

33:51.500 --> 33:54.959
HER BLOOD, AND THE BLOOD
OF YOUR GRANDCHILD.

34:00.750 --> 34:03.834
CONSTABLE SARA MILLER'S FAMILY
WAS DEVASTATED BY HER DEATH,

34:03.834 --> 34:05.750
NONE MORE SO
THAN HER BROTHER CURTIS.

34:05.750 --> 34:08.625
HE ATTENDED DAVID LUBBE'S TRIAL
EVERY DAY

34:08.625 --> 34:10.500
AND LATER RECEIVED A DISCHARGE

34:10.500 --> 34:13.375
FROM THE SOUTH AFRICAN
NATIONAL DEFENSE FORCE

34:13.375 --> 34:16.166
BASED ON CONCERNS
ABOUT HIS MENTAL HEALTH.

34:16.166 --> 34:18.583
SAYS HERE MILLER'S PARENTS
PASSED AWAY IN 2000

34:18.583 --> 34:19.959
AND CURTIS INHERITED
THE FAMILY HOME

34:19.959 --> 34:21.542
IN AUCKLAND PARK.

34:21.542 --> 34:23.041
WHICH S.F.B. OFFICERS
JUST RAIDED.

34:23.041 --> 34:24.375
THERE WAS NOTHING THERE.

34:24.375 --> 34:25.625
LOOKS LIKE HE CLEARED OUT
WEEKS AGO.

34:25.625 --> 34:27.250
SO CURTIS MILLER'S IN THE WIND,

34:27.250 --> 34:29.625
AND WE STILL DON'T KNOW WHO THIS
THIRD PRETORIUS AGENT IS.

34:29.625 --> 34:31.875
HIS CHILDREN ARE IN
IMMINENT DANGER.
MONTY,

34:31.875 --> 34:33.834
you've held off notifying
Armand Smit and his wife

34:33.834 --> 34:35.291
about Brandon's rescue,
right?

34:35.291 --> 34:38.041
AS YOU REQUESTED.
SO NOW WE HAVE NO CHOICE.

34:38.041 --> 34:40.959
THE ONLY WAY TO GET THE NAME
OF THAT THIRD PRETORIUS AGENT

34:40.959 --> 34:43.125
IS FOR MONTY TO GET IT
FROM SMIT HIMSELF.

34:43.125 --> 34:46.125
BUT DOESN'T HE ACTUALLY HAVE TO
ADMIT WHO HE IS FIRST?

34:46.125 --> 34:48.500
THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT
HE HAS TO DO.

34:50.458 --> 34:52.709
SO...I HAVE NEWS
ABOUT YOUR SON.

34:54.041 --> 34:55.709
WE RESCUED HIM.

34:55.709 --> 34:57.709
HE'S ALIVE AND RECOVERING
AT BRISBANE HOSPITAL.

34:57.709 --> 35:00.083
OH!

35:01.375 --> 35:04.417
HE WAS FOUND
WITH ROWAN BOSCH...

35:04.417 --> 35:07.166
OR WHAT'S LEFT OF HIM.

35:09.375 --> 35:11.583
ROWAN BOSCH?

35:11.583 --> 35:14.917
IS -- IS HE RELATED
TO THAT WOMAN YOU SHOWED US?

35:14.917 --> 35:16.917
YES.

35:16.917 --> 35:18.583
HE WAS HER FATHER.

35:18.583 --> 35:22.208
HE WORKED WITH YOUR HUSBAND
IN PRETORIUS.

35:22.208 --> 35:23.750
PRETORIUS?

35:23.750 --> 35:25.750
THIS IS HARASSMENT.

35:25.750 --> 35:28.125
I'LL SUE YOU
AND THE BUREAU.

35:28.125 --> 35:29.959
ARMAND, WHAT'S GOING ON?

35:29.959 --> 35:33.041
YOU GO AHEAD AND DO THAT,
MR. SMIT.

35:33.041 --> 35:34.875
BUT RIGHT NOW IS WHAT
MY GRANDMOTHER LIKES TO CALL

35:34.875 --> 35:36.291
A "COME TO JESUS" TIME.

35:36.291 --> 35:38.458
THERE ARE LIVES AT STAKE.

35:38.458 --> 35:41.625
I KNOW YOU AND BOSCH WERE
TWO OF THREE MEN IN PRETORIUS.

35:41.625 --> 35:43.583
I'M GONNA NEED
THAT THIRD MAN'S NAME,

35:43.583 --> 35:47.125
BEFORE HIS CHILDREN SUFFER
THE SAME FATE

35:47.125 --> 35:50.625
AS KURT...

35:50.625 --> 35:54.834
AND LARA...

35:54.834 --> 35:56.875
AND TIMOTHY,

35:56.875 --> 36:00.125
YOUR OWN SON.

36:02.458 --> 36:04.000
WHAT DID YOU DO?

36:04.000 --> 36:06.041
NOTHING.
I DID NOTHING WRONG.

36:06.041 --> 36:08.125
SERIOUSLY? YOU'RE JUST
GONNA LET THE BLOOD

36:08.125 --> 36:10.208
OF THAT MAN'S CHILDREN
BE ON YOUR HANDS?

36:10.208 --> 36:11.500
LET'S GO, CAMILLE.

36:11.500 --> 36:13.000
OH, YOU THINK THE BLOOD

36:13.000 --> 36:14.333
WILL JUST BLEND IN
WITH ALL THE REST, HUH?

36:14.333 --> 36:17.000
HEY! LOOK AT HIM!

36:21.500 --> 36:24.709
NOW GIVE ME
THE MAN'S NAME.

36:29.375 --> 36:31.875
I KNEW THERE WERE SECRETS
ABOUT YOUR PAST,

36:31.875 --> 36:33.750
BUT...I LOVED YOU,

36:33.750 --> 36:38.500
SO I NEVER ASKED YOU
ANY QUESTIONS.

36:38.500 --> 36:40.875
WE KNEW A BOSCH ONCE.

36:40.875 --> 36:44.208
WHEN WE FIRST MET.

36:44.208 --> 36:46.083
AND THERE WAS ANOTHER MAN.

36:46.083 --> 36:48.750
CAMILLE, PLEASE.
HIS NAME WAS...

36:48.750 --> 36:50.875
COETZEE.

36:50.875 --> 36:54.041
NOAH COETZEE.

36:54.041 --> 36:56.792
HE MAY STILL LIVE
IN BLOEMFONTEIN.

36:59.083 --> 37:01.333
THANK YOU.

37:12.583 --> 37:14.625
PA?

37:14.625 --> 37:16.125
NO!
PA?

37:16.125 --> 37:18.166
LYDIA! GET OUT!

37:18.166 --> 37:20.375
UHH!

37:20.375 --> 37:21.834
AAH!

37:21.834 --> 37:24.250
NO! NO! OH!

37:24.250 --> 37:26.500
MY BABY, PLEASE!
PLEASE, MY BABY!

37:26.500 --> 37:29.583
NO, PLEASE.
NOAH, LOOK AT THIS.

37:29.583 --> 37:31.208
MY BABY, PLEASE.

37:31.208 --> 37:34.834
LET HER GO. KILL ME.
I DID IT.

37:34.834 --> 37:38.750
WHAT DID YOU DO? TELL ME.
TELL HER.

37:40.291 --> 37:43.041
♪♪

37:43.041 --> 37:46.375
I MURDERED YOUR SISTER.

37:46.375 --> 37:49.500
ARMAND, ROWAN, AND I,
WE AMBUSHED HER

37:49.500 --> 37:54.041
WHEN SHE WAS ON PATROL
IN AZARIA.

37:54.041 --> 37:56.250
I WANTED TO SHOOT HER,

37:56.250 --> 37:58.917
BUT ROWAN WANTED TO MAKE IT
LOOK MORE ZULU.

37:58.917 --> 38:01.625
SO ARMAND STABBED HER.

38:01.625 --> 38:04.709
AND I KNEW THE YOUNG MAN
WE COULD PIN IT ON.

38:07.709 --> 38:09.417
FBI.
Zwane: LET HER GO.

38:09.417 --> 38:11.125
GET OUT.

38:11.125 --> 38:12.875
CURTIS, WE KNOW THE TRUTH
ABOUT YOUR SISTER'S MURDER,

38:12.875 --> 38:15.500
AND WE'RE HERE NOW TO PUNISH
THE MEN RESPONSIBLE,

38:15.500 --> 38:17.583
SO YOU DON'T HAVE TO HURT THIS
WOMAN AND HER BABY. LET HER GO.

38:17.583 --> 38:20.458
YOU CANNOT PUNISH THESE MEN.
THEY'RE PROTECTED FOREVER.

38:20.458 --> 38:22.458
NO, CURTIS,
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

38:22.458 --> 38:24.750
SO I WILL END THEM FOREVER.

38:24.750 --> 38:26.625
PLEASE.

38:26.625 --> 38:28.291
NO!

38:55.458 --> 38:58.500
♪♪

39:00.834 --> 39:04.291
YOU HAVE A GOOD TEAM.
YOU SHOULD BE VERY PROUD.

39:04.291 --> 39:06.959
I AM.
I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU THINK

39:06.959 --> 39:10.250
MY METHODS DIMINISH THE SCIENCE
OF CRIMINAL PROFILING.

39:10.250 --> 39:12.875
IT'S NOT MAGIC.
NO, IT ISN'T,

39:12.875 --> 39:14.542
BUT I WISH
YOU COULD UNDERSTAND

39:14.542 --> 39:16.917
THAT YOU AND I ARE NOT
AS DIFFERENT AS YOU THINK.

39:16.917 --> 39:20.458
IN EVERY FIBER,
IN EVERY PRINT,

39:20.458 --> 39:23.792
IN EVERY DROP OF BLOOD
LEFT BEHIND,

39:23.792 --> 39:26.709
ARE NOT THE DEAD SPEAKING
TO YOU, JACK?

39:26.709 --> 39:29.959
IN A MANNER OF SPEAKING,
YES.

39:29.959 --> 39:32.250
BUT MAYBE
WHAT'S MOST IMPORTANT

39:32.250 --> 39:36.041
IS THAT I SPEAK FOR THEM.

39:45.333 --> 39:48.208
♪♪

39:57.500 --> 39:59.875
BRANDON?

40:03.166 --> 40:05.625
Camille: OH, MY BABY.

40:05.625 --> 40:08.000
MOM.

40:08.000 --> 40:10.583
ARMAND SMIT...

40:10.583 --> 40:12.417
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST FOR MURDER.

40:12.417 --> 40:15.291
MURDER? WHAT MURDER?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

40:15.291 --> 40:17.834
STOP!
I HAVE COMPLETE IMMUNITY.

40:17.834 --> 40:20.500
